entry.title: DIY a macbook pro charge for car power
entry.content:
Adjust this boost module to boost the car voltage from 12 volts to 22 volts, and then connect another PD fast charge module. Be sure to add another fan to the PD module. When charging at 60W, the heat is serious, so I burned a PD module.
